Package: contextual
Type: Package
Title: Context-aware hierarchical messaging and auto-numbering for R console output
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", , "benjaminpeeters@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5095-2021"))
Description: Provides context-aware messaging and hierarchical document structuring 
    for R analysis workflows. Features include automatic hierarchical numbering,
    formatted messages with consistent styling, context-aware text indentation,
    and smart execution reset detection. Part of the macroverse R ecosystem.
